Title: Beethoven Symphony No. 2,Schubert Symphony No. 9 - London Classical Players - Norrington (RAH, 1989)
Description:
0:00:00 Beethoven Symphony No. 2
0:33:39 Schubert Symphony No. 9
1:30:54 Schubert Rosamunde - Ballet Music No. 2

These performances were given as part of the 19898 season of BBC Promenade Concerts at the Royal Albert Hall, London on 21 August 1989.

London Classical Players
conducted by
Roger Norrington

For more details see:
https://www.bbc.co.uk/events/ewwzc8
